Figs. 1
arrow, 2 ); exobothridial seta ( ex ) inserted posteriad in ; rostral seta ( ro ) inserted posteriad lamellar seta; lamellar seta ( le ) curves ventrad, inserted at anterior base of strong transverse prelamellar ridge (
